---
import MarketingLayout from "../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";
---

<MarketingLayout title="Terms of Service - BuffBook" description="Terms of Service for BuffBook">
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-foreground mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-muted-foreground">
      <p class="mb-4">Last updated: June 2026</p>
      
      <div class="p-6 bg-destructive/10 border border-destructive/20 rounded-xl mb-8 text-foreground font-medium">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-destructive mb-2">Medical Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>BuffBook is for educational and informational purposes only. The information provided is not intended as a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified health provider before starting any new training program. You assume all risk of injury associated with following any training advice, concepts, or custom plans provided by BuffBook.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">By accessing or using BuffBook, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, do not use our services.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">2. Custom Coaching Plans</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Custom mesocycle plans are bespoke digital products. Because these plans are built from scratch specifically for your unique biomechanics and goals, <strong>all sales are final and non-refundable once the assessment has been submitted and work has begun.</strong></p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">The free content provided on BuffBook is our intellectual property. You may not scrape, copy, redistribute, or sell the written content, frameworks, or custom plans provided to you without explicit permission.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mt-8 mb-4">4. Account Termination</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account at any time for violations of these Terms, including but not limited to the unauthorized redistribution of our content.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</MarketingLayout>
